tool_description: TheAudioDB.com is a community driven database of audio metadata. It is our aim to be the most simple and accurate source of Music data from all over the world. We also provide a repository of data that can be used in various types of HTPC software to make your viewing experience more visually appealing.

api_list.code:
import requests

url = "https://theaudiodb.p.rapidapi.com/mostloved.php?format=track"

headers = {
            "X-RapidAPI-Key": "SIGN-UP-FOR-KEY",
            "X-RapidAPI-Host": "theaudiodb.p.rapidapi.com"
        }

response = requests.get(url, headers=headers)
print(response.json())
